            <title>[CASSANDRA-2162] cassandra-cli --keyspace option doesn&apos;t work properly when used with authentication</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-2162</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The logic to select the keyspace is applied before authentication credentials are processed in cassandra-cli. This leads to a &quot;Keyspace FOO not found&quot; message at login for a keyspace that exists.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
